	Fixes <https://savannah.gnu.org/bugs/?57546>.

2020-01-17  G. Branden Robinson <g.branden.robinson@gmail.com>

	* src/preproc/refer/refer.1.man (See Also):
	* src/utils/indxbib/indxbib.1.man (See Also):
