2015-08-05  Bernd Warken  <groff-bernd.warken-72@web.de>

	* Makefile.am, arch/mingw/mingw.am, arch/misc/misc.am,
	* contrib/eqn2graph/eqn2graph.am, contrib/grap2graph/grap2graph,
