	to `$PERL', which has the same content.  But `$PERL' suits to
	`AX_PROG_PERL_VERSION' in m4 macro `GROFF_PERL' in `m4/groff.m4'.

	* src/utils/afmtodit/Makefile.sub,
	* src/devices/gropdf/gropdf.pl,
